{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_48","type":"agent_message","text":"Implementation plan:\n1. Add orchestration-aware tools: `AgentTool` (spawn worker from `WorkerTaskSpec`) and `TaskStopTool` (cancel running task).\n2. Add a shared worker manager in `ccode-tools` that routes `WorkerResultNotification` into `MultiAgentOrchestrator::handle_notification`.\n3. Wire both tools in bootstrap with coordinator-mode gating from `CLAUDE_CODE_COORDINATOR_MODE`.\n4. Update CLI/TUI output helpers to render worker status labels from tool payloads.\n5. Add/extend tests for tool behavior and status rendering, then run fmt/clippy/test and commit."}}
